com.innolabs.spydroid

Class SMSListeners

  • java.lang.Object
    • Service
      • com.innolabs.spydroid.SMSListeners

  • public class SMSListeners
extends Service
    SMS Listener Service is a service used to SPY the SMS logs from the device. All INCOMING, OUTGOING SMS messages are logged and store to a database in this service.
    Author:
    Srikanth Rao
    See Also:
    Service
